<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background-color: #B8860B; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
    .content { padding: 20px; }
    .tracking-info { background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0; }
    .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; color: #666; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Shipping Update</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Dear {{userName}},</p>
      <p>There has been an update to your order (ID: {{orderId}}).</p>
      
      <div class="tracking-info">
        <h2>Shipping Details:</h2>
        <p><strong>Status:</strong> {{status}}</p>
        <p><strong>Tracking Number:</strong> {{trackingNumber}}</p>
        <p><strong>Estimated Delivery:</strong> {{estimatedDelivery}}</p>
      </div>

      <p>You can track your shipment using the tracking number above.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Best regards,<br>Car Grip Team</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 